collectionMetadata.name: Number of children at 2 years of age immunised by sector and vaccine type
collectionMetadata.description:
The table/figure shows the number of children who were immunised by the public and private healthcare sector for children at 2 years of age in Singapore. 

The numbers will be updated annually due to ongoing retrospective case collection.
